                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#24v">24v</locus>: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ እቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡
